<xhtml:html xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" xsl:version="2.0">
	<xhtml:head>
		<xhtml:title>Can not display form</xhtml:title>
		<xhtml:style type="text/css">
			body {
			text-align:center;
			}
			#container {
			margin:0px auto 0px auto;
			width:400px;
			border:1px solid #000000;
			}
			#notes {
			font-size: 9px;
			}
		</xhtml:style>
	</xhtml:head>
	<xhtml:body>
		<xhtml:h3>
			<xsl:text>Could not retrieve form</xsl:text>
		</xhtml:h3>
		<xhtml:div id="container">
			<xhtml:img style="float:left" src="/images/warning_load.gif"/>
			<xhtml:p>
				Please check that the form for the url: <br/>
				<b><xsl:value-of select="/task/url"/></b><br/>
				has been properly deployed properly on the server.
			</xhtml:p>
		</xhtml:div>
		<xhtml:div id="notes">
			<xhtml:p>
				Using this <a href="/wds/AbsenceRequest/AbsenceRequest.xform">link</a>, you can check it is deployed on the server deployment service.
			</xhtml:p>	
		</xhtml:div>
	</xhtml:body>
</xhtml:html>